  "text": "The image decoder then mirrors the image encoder, using upsampling instead of downsampling, and deconvolutions instead of convolutions, mapping the bottleneck tensor into a w×h-dimensional output image. In contrast to the \"subpixel\" layers [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] used in [CITATION_3] , we use standard deconvolutions for simplicity.",
